-- India Threatens to Ban Blackberry Services as Security Risk, Mint Reports
-- Thomas Abraham
-- 2010-07-29T01:27:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/india-threatens-to-ban-blackberry-services-as-security-risk-mint-reports.html

          
          
             India’s home ministry is considering
banning Blackberry mobile services as Research in Motion Ltd.
didn’t provide it with details of users, posing a threat to
national security, the Mint newspaper reported, citing a
government official it didn’t identify.  
